dent  group ceo products plantation motors industrial property logistics revenue rm billion  operating income rm billion  net income rm billion  number of employees over  parent permodalan nasional berhad website wwwsimedarbycom sime darby berhad myx  is a major malaysiabased multinational conglomerate involved in  core sectors plantations property industrial motors and logistics sime darby is listed on the main board of bursa malaysia securities berhad it has vested interests and close relationships with the malaysian government  it has assisted the malaysian government by buying the management of the sarawak land development board sldb made loss in   sime darby turned the financial situation and sold it to government owned sarawak plantation services contents  background  sime darby and co limited  guthrie  golden hope  merger  businesses  plantation  property  industrial  motoring  logistics  healthcare  other businesses  controversies  see also  references  external links backgroundedit the modern sime darby berhad corporation was created in  through a merger of three companies sime darby and co limitededit in october  british businessmen william sime and henry darby established sime darby and co a fledgling player in the lucrative rubber industry the company later diversified to cultivating palm oil and cocoa and met with enormous success at the time of the companys founding william middleton sime was a yearold scottish adventurer and fortune seeker he had two failed ventures behind him – one in importexport business and the other in coffee plantations – when he left his job as a mercantile assistant in singapore henry darby was a wealthy yearold english banker who owned property in northern malaya a senior partner of the audit firm of the sime darby group was found dead in september  in two suicide letters he alleged he was doped and deceived by dennis pinder chairman and managing director of sime darby related to the audit of sime darby subsequently dennis pinder was alleged that he misappropriated over s million at that time sime darby was one of the largest companies in singapore and malaysia pinder was jailed after pleading guilty to criminal breach of trust in october  in  sime darby holdings was acquired by malaysian investors – mainly through tradewinds malaysia sendirian berhad in december  with the incorporation of two new malaysian entities sime darby berhad sdb and consolidated plantations berhad cpb sime darby moved its headquarters to kuala lumpur and became a malaysian registered and managed concern guthrieedit main article guthrie company the company was founded in singapore in  by alexander guthrie it was the first british trading company in south east asia guthrie introduced rubber and oil palm in malaysia in  and  respectively guthrie group was made a public company in  and was subsequently listed on the kuala lumpur stock exchange klse in  in what was then the largest public issue in malaysia golden hopeedit main article golden hope in  harrisons and crosfield a british tea and coffee trading company purchased several small estates in malaysia for £ and amalgamated them to form the golden hope rubber estate in  harrisons and crosfield sold three large plantation groups – golden hope pataling and london asiatic – to malaysian concerns for £ million the business was renamed golden hope plantations berhad in  after pemodalan nasional berhad took majority equity of the company its interests originally were in tropical agriculture but while plantations have remained a core business interest the company has diversified into other areas including glycerine manufacture fruit juices and real estate the group now has  subsidiaries based in seven countries the main estate and plantations are carey island and banting in selangor mergeredit in january  the three malaysian giants sime darby guthrie and golden hope merged into the vehicle entity named synergy drive and on  november  synergy drive was renamed sime darby berhad sime darby had a land bank of  hectares in  the malaysian governmentlinked company amanah saham was the largest stakeholder in  followed by the governments employees provident fund and the governmentrun permodalan nasional berhad pnb the national capitalization agency ceo of the firm was datuk mohd bakke saleh who was also the ceo of bank islam another governmentlinked company in  businessesedit sime darby is an international conglomerate involved in many types of businesses ranging from agriculture to ports management plantation sector remains the most important sector for the company plantationedit sime darby palm oil storage tanks in kunak sabah sime darby operates palm oil and rubber plantations in malaysia indonesia and liberia plantations are sime darbys largest revenue generator accounting for the majority of the groups profits in recent years sime darby is one of the largest palm oil producers in the world supplying about  million metric tonnes or  of world supply the company has a total planted area over  hectares and a land bank over  hectares about twothirds of the sime darbys palm oil production comes from malaysia and onethird from indonesia the companys recently developed estates in liberia were not yet in production as of  a related company in the sime darby group sime darby biodiesel sdn bhd produces biodiesel from crude palm oil propertyedit sime darby property is involved in the property development business in eight countries namely malaysia singapore indonesia philippines vietnam peoples republic of china australia and united kingdom industrialedit the company is involved in the purchasing leasing and selling of industrial equipment such as caterpillar inc heavy duty trucks and tractors motoringedit the company has motor dealerships in eight countries it owns auto bavaria in malaysia which sells bmws and minis with partnership with ford it sells fords cars and trucks together with the land rover brand besides that it is the main dealership of porsche and alfa romeo in malaysia it is also a major bmw dealer in singapore australia new zealand india and thailand in southern china the company sells bmw and rollsroyce in addition sime darby coowns inokom corp bhd a jointventure with hyundai motor company which assembles and sells hyundai vehicles in malaysia logisticsedit the company is involved in ports  logistics and water management in the province of shandong in the northeastern china region healthcareedit the healthcare division has a hospital and college of its own the sime darby medical centre formerly known as subang jaya medical centre and its college formerly known as sjmc academy of nursing and health sciences was established in  and currently is known as sime darby nursing and health sciences college other businessesedit tesco stores malaysia sdn bhd is a jointventure between sime darby berhad and tesco plc its inception in  saw sime darby hold a  per cent stake in the jointventure tesco currently operates  hypermarkets in malaysia controversiesedit sime darby has been accused of violating the land rights of local communities in liberia where they hold a concession for  hectares of farmland local environmental and human rights groups have called sime darbys contract with the liberian government a land grab and say that the contract does not account for the ownership rights of the rural communities who live inside the concession area in  representatives of one community made a formal complaint to the roundtable on sustainable palm oil rspo and in  a group of communities signed onto a statement criticising the contract sime darby contends that its contract is legal and was completed with a democratically elected government saying there is no evidence whatsoever that it violates human rights for their part civil society activists in liberia state that the contract makes no protection for the land rights of rural communities and have called for renegotiation in  sime darby was accused of lighting some of the fires on indonesian plantations that caused widespread pollution issues in malaysia and singapore however the company denied being responsible for the fires it has made public commitments not to develop on peat  see alsoedit sime darby fc referencesedit  a b c annual report  pdf sime derby retrieved  march    a b c d helena varkkey the haze problem in southeast asia abingdon routledge  p   malaysia targets alternative fuels market the telegraph  december  retrieved  december    a b lim peter h l   chronicle of singapore fifty years of headline news editions didier millet isbn  retrieved  august    a b c waterhouse ronald child of another century the radcliffe press isbn  retrieved  august    transnational corporations from asian developing countries the internationalisation characteristics and business strategies of sime darby berhad international journal of business science and applied management january  retrieved  december    a b answers  the most trusted place for answering lifes questions answerscom retrieved  january    aim collection description retrieved  january    helena varkkey the haze problem in southeast asia abingdon routledge  p   helena varkkey the haze problem in southeast asia abingdon routledge  p   board of directors sime darby retrieved  january    annual report  pdf sime darby p  retrieved  february    annual report  pdf sime darby p  retrieved  february    annual report  pdf sime darby p  retrieved  february    sime darby takes the lead in biofuel sin chew retrieved  september    liberia sime darby agrees to pay one million  webmaster frontpageafrica  frontpageafrica retrieved  january    open letter to friends of the earth sime darby  fact sheet sime darby and land grabs in liberia friends of the earth  sime darby denies any fires in indonesian plantations retrieved  january    helena varkkey the haze problem in southeast asia abingdon routledge  p  external linksedit official site v t e constituents of the ftse bursa malaysia